Kevin Rankin (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kevin_Rankin_(actor) 0 Kevin Rankin (born April 18, 1976) is an American actor. He is best known for his roles as Tyler Briggs in the NBC series Trauma, Roe Sanders in the CBS series Unforgettable, Kenny in the AMC series Breaking Bad, and Derek "Devil" Lennox in the FX TV series Justified.
